name: 2.1.2.Final
body:
- [**Bug**][**2.1.x**] UI filter malfunction in 2.1.0 and 2.1.1 versions [#1967](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1967)
- [**closed**] UI won't load after successful keycloak authentication [#1966](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1966)
- [**Bug**] Apicurio Registry UI: Wrong redirects to http instead of https [#1959](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1959)
- [**Bug**][**2.1.x**] typo in anonymous_readonly evnironment variable in documentation [#1958](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1958)
- [**closed**] Support for Google Protobuf well known types [#1924](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1924)
- [**Bug**] keycloak, roles, logout does not work with 2.1.0.Final but works with 2.0.0.Final [#1888](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1888)
- [**Question**] Apicurio/confluent compatibility issues [#1874](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1874)
- [**Enhancement**][**Impacts Documentation**][**Beginner Friendly**] Allow configuration of consumer group prefix [#1591](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1591)
